Describe image in file
           Dockerfile

docker build image
            docker build -t=radulenko/overall-tests .

docker run container
            docker run -it -v ${PWD}/target/allure-results:/home/selemium-docker/allure-results radulenko/overall-tests

run tests from container on selenium grid on my local machine

            java -Dbrowser=remote -DseleniumHubHost=192.168.0.121 -cp 'libs/*' RunTest loginTests.LoginTestWithPageObject

            java -Dbrowser=remote -Denv=aqa -DseleniumHubHost=192.168.0.121 -cp 'libs/*' RunTest suits.RegressionSuite -threadcount=2

Run test from image
        docker run -e BROWSER=remote -e ENV=aqa -e SELENIUM_HUB_HOST=192.168.0.121 -e SUITES=suits.RegressionSuite -e THREAD_COUNT=2 -v ${PWD}/target/allure-results:/home/selemium-docker/allure-results radulenko/overall-tests

Docker delete unused images
        docker system prune -f

